node.text: @florencesjah Hehehe sure go ahead and get it!! It's done boiled 😉

[#BeHomeNowSG — Hope it isn't becoming too restless this Stay Home period, 3 more weeks to a little freedom yea🤞🏻]
•
You might have already noticed that friends and family member amongst you are becoming their own chef 🧑🏻‍🍳 and I encourage you to get up and make a meal for yourself too! 😄
•
For me, I prefer making western-style dishes and thus made it for my family after the end of my university semester! This dish, Honey Glazed Chicken with Creamy Mashed Potatoes and Brocolli was something I've always pictured together and I'm glad that I've finally brought it to life 🤗 If you're curious to make it yourself, ask me for this recipe anytime!! 😉
We’re all leaving this quarantine as chefs 😂
@mysweetlittletooth Yes indeed!! Thanks babe! Same here, love those really creamy ones especially 😋😉
Looks simple but good! Love mashed potatoes 😋😋
@ilove_mytwoboys Thank you, I'm so glad to make it look and taste good ☺️🤗
@storify.me Yup we should!! Great tip right there 😊🙌🏻
And get an air fryer if you can! Makes cooking so much easier!
@leylaleeeeeeee Aww thanks babe!! Hehe yay, Im glad it all turned out well ☺️🤗
Nice!!!! The chicken looks so yummm!!!!! Also the mashed potato😍😍😍😍
@city2shoredreamer Definitely!! We're all cooking more this stay home period ☺️🙌🏻
@thevegetariancouple Ohmy then maybe u would love to try some of my mine ☺️🤗
Yum! That's a perfect meal right there
@_forkitover_ Nicee, I prefer it without the skin! But if it's baked potatoes, skin on is fine 😉🙌🏻
I love making my mashed potatoes with the skin on 😊❤️
@eatandtravelwithus Thank you!! 🤗 Yay I'm glad it turned out well ☺️
The best type of home cooked meal 😋
@dashofting Yay im glad it turned out well!! ☺️🤗
I love the look of that mashed potato! yum!
@dingsleepy Hahahha 😂 Yaa should be, we have been in the CB period for too long, starting to see things 🤪
I tot the potato was an omelette omg. Must be circuit breaker getting to me 😂
@stefoodography Yay thanks babe, I'm glad it turned out well!! 🤗
@nycfoodcoop Yass I wish I could make some more and let u try some 🙆🏻‍♀️
@florencesjah Hehehe sure go ahead and get it!! It's done boiled 😉
